Package: lfsfeed
Title: Monitor Eurostat Statistics-Update RSS for Labour Force Survey Bulk Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Eurostat LFS Feed", "Author", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "noreply@example.org")
Description: Polls the Eurostat dissemination 'statistics-update' RSS feed,
    filters items for Labour Force Survey ('LFS') datasets, and downloads
    the corresponding bulk TSV ('.tsv.gz') files via the Eurostat SDMX 2.1
    bulk endpoint. Maintains a small per-cache state file so subsequent
    runs only fetch datasets whose pubDate is newer than the last seen
    timestamp, and returns a manifest tibble describing every attempted
    download.
